{{Infobox_NPC |name = Gustav |image = XC3 Gustav Icon.png |personality = |time_active = |gender = Male |race = |age = 7th Term |location = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Fort O'Virbus]]) }} '''Gustav''' is a NPC in {{XC3}} who can be found in [[Fort O'Virbus]].
== Overview == Gustav is the superintendent of the [[Ether Mine (XC3)|Ether Mine]] on [[Hovering Reef 1 (XC3)|Hovering Reef 1]]. He used his position to secretly siphon ether in order to create an army of [[Levnis]]es, and commit an assault [[Agnus]] in hopes of sparking another war, but was ultimately unsuccessful in starting a war. {{clr}}
