{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Gyrinus |image = XC3 Gyrinus.jpg |caption = Gyrinus |category = [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Levnis]] |level = 48 |area = [[Agnus Castle Barbican]] |spawntime = Story |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = |gold = |hp = |strength = |healing = |dexterity = |agility = |physdef = |ethdef = |critrate = |guardrate-front = |guardrate-side = |guardrate-back = }} '''Gyrinus''' is a [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] in {{XC3}}. They are [[Agnus|Agnian]] [[Levnis]]es. Three Gyrinuses appear during [[Chapter 5 (XC3)|Chapter 5]] at [[Agnus Castle Barbican]] in the [[Cadensia Region]], but only a single level 48 one is fought. When they appear, they are described as the [[Agnus Castle|Castle]] Guard. {{clr}}
